schedule.description: In a world racing toward AI dominance, thereâ€™s one thing the machines can't replicate: the boundless spark of human creativity. Join me for a deep dive into why "intelligent" AI still can't outthink human imagination - and how developers and innovators have always thrived by embracing the unknown.
